Social inclusion and empowerment outcomes.
Environmental Sustainability
Climate mitigation/adaptation, biodiversity, water usage, reduced emissions, soil health, land use change, ocean ecosystems
Environmental outcomes (GHG reduction, soil fertility, biodiversity).
Food Security & Nutrition
Food access, availability, utilization, sovereignty, affordability, dietary diversity
Nutrition, food availability or access, reduced malnutrition.
Inducing Policy Change
Reducing food waste, acceptability, malnutrition prevention, new laws passed/modified, budgetary changes, institutional changes, research & development
Policy reforms, institutional or budgetary shifts.

Evidence & Citation Rules
Every extraction must have at least one citation with a page number.
Evidence text must be ≤150 words and drawn exactly from the document.
If uncertain or incomplete, mark needs_review_flag=true.
No inference, no summarization, no paraphrasing.
Interventions and outcomes may appear on the same page — allowed and encouraged.
If both PAD and PID exist for the same Project ID:
Prioritize PAD and ignore PID content.
Set duplicate_flag=true for PID (no extraction).

Markdown Report Output (Per Document)
# [Project Title] (World Bank, [Year], [Country])

| IFI | Project Title | Country | Year | Doc Type | Project ID |
|-----|---------------|---------|------|----------|-------------|

